      • vars

        public VarResolverBuilder vars(Class<?>... vars)
        Register new variables with this resolver.
        Parameters:
        vars - The variable resolver classes. These classes must subclass from Var and have no-arg constructors.
        Returns:
        This object (for method chaining).

      • defaultVars

        public VarResolverBuilder defaultVars()
        Adds the default variables to this builder.

        The default variables are:

        • SystemPropertiesVar
        • EnvVariablesVar
        • ArgsVar
        • ManifestFileVar
        • SwitchVar
        • IfVar
        • CoalesceVar
        • PatternMatchVar
        • UpperCaseVar
        • LowerCaseVar
        • NotEmptyVar
        Returns:
        This object (for method chaining).

      • contextObject

        public VarResolverBuilder contextObject(String name,
                                        Object object)
        Associates a context object with this resolver.

        A context object is essentially some environmental object that doesn't change but is used by vars to customize output.

        Parameters:
        name - The name of the context object.
        object - The context object.
        Returns:
        This object (for method chaining).

      • contextObjects

        public VarResolverBuilder contextObjects(Map<String,Object> map)
        Associates multiple context objects with this resolver.

        A context object is essentially some environmental object that doesn't change but is used by vars to customize output.

        Parameters:
        map - A map of context objects keyed by their name.
        Returns:
        This object (for method chaining).
